subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Matt Kenseth will try to become the first driver since Jeff Gordon in 1997 to win the first two races of the year when he competes at the Auto Club 500 in Fontana, Calif.
